 for Financial Assistance in RU\">Applying for Financial Assistance in RU<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-7\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/ru-online-application-form\/#Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_RU_Admission_2024\" title=\"Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for RU Admission 2024?\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for RU Admission 2024?<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>Table of Contents<\/strong><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648186\">About the Rhodes University (RU) Online Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648187\"><strong>How to Apply for RU Application 2024<\/strong><\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648188\">Documents Required for RU Admission Application 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648189\">RU Application Fees 2024<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648190\">Application Deadline:<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648191\">Applying for Financial Assistance in RU<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"#_Toc80648192\">Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for RU Admission 2024?<\/a><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"about-the-rhodes-university-ru-online-application-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"About_the_Rhodes_University_RU_Online_Application_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80648186\"><\/a>About the Rhodes University (RU) Online Application 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>This is to inform all and sundry that the management of the Rhodes University(RU) is inviting applications from interested and suitably qualified students (Indigenes and International) for admission into undergraduate and postgraduate programmes for the 2024 academic year.<\/p>\n<p>Before you apply, see the know the actual programs (Courses) available for the 2024 admission.<\/p>\n<p><a name=\"_Toc80648187\"><\/a><strong>How to Apply for RU Application 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h4 id=\"%c2%b7-visit-here\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"%C2%B7_Visit_here\"><\/span>\u00b7\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 Visit <a href=\"http:\/\/www.ru.ac.za\/admissiongateway\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">here<\/a><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>select undergraduate\/postgraduate\/semester study abroad<\/li>\n<li>Create an Account with your valid email on the portal.<\/li>\n<li>Fill all necessary forms.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"documents-required-for-ru-online-application-form-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Documents_Required_for_RU_Online_Application_Form_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80648188\"><\/a>Documents Required for RU Online Application Form 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Valid Email<\/li>\n<li>South African Identity Number<\/li>\n<li>Passport Number (International Students)<\/li>\n<li>Final School results<\/li>\n<li>Valid Passport or Identity Document or Birth Certificate<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"ru-application-fees-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"RU_Application_Fees_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80648189\"><\/a>RU Application Fees 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Pay a non-refundable application fee of R100 for South African citizens<\/li>\n<li>Pay a Non-refundable application fee for foreign citizens of R100<\/li>\n<li>Payments to be made before closing dates<\/li>\n<li>Ensure to use your Person Number or T Number as a reference<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"application-deadline\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Application_Deadline\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80648190\"><\/a>Application Deadline:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>30\u00a0September 2024<\/strong><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"applying-for-financial-assistance-in-ru\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Applying_for_Financial_Assistance_in_RU\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80648191\"><\/a>Applying for Financial Assistance in RU<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Interested applicant can apply for financial assistance (Scholarship) through the NSFAS application portal<a href=\"https:\/\/www.ru.ac.za\/studentfeesandfinancialaid\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https:\/\/www.ru.ac.za\/studentfeesandfinancialaid\/<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ru.ac.za\/studentfeesandfinancialaid\/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to Apply<\/a><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"is-national-benchmark-test-nbt-required-for-ru-admission-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Is_National_Benchmark_Test_NBT_required_for_RU_Admission_2024\"><\/span><a name=\"_Toc80648192\"><\/a>Is National Benchmark Test (NBT) required for RU Admission 2024?<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Yes.<\/strong><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"RU Online Application Form 2024 for Admission into Rhodes University, RU Application fees, Programs (Courses), Application Status, Closing&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1126,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[65],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1125"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1125"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1125\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1125"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=112